OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1778937070
OL,3,CStudent dies and two others being
OL,4,Ctreated after meningitis outbreak in
OL,5,CReading
OL,7,FA Henley College student has died and
OL,8,Ftwo other people are being treated at
OL,9,Fthe Royal Berkshire Hospital following
OL,10,Fa meningitis outbreak amongst young
OL,11,Fpeople in Reading.
OL,13,FSpecialists from the UK Health
OL,14,FSecurity Agency (UKHSA) South East
OL,15,Fconfirmed that close contacts of the
OL,16,Fcases are being offered antibiotics as
OL,17,Fa precaution.
OL,19,FOne case has been confirmed as
OL,20,FMeningitis B and other tests are being
OL,21,Fcarried out.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
