FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1778937070
OL,3,CStudent dies and two others being
OL,4,Ctreated after meningitis outbreak in
OL,5,CReading
OL,7,FThe UKHSA said that students and
OL,8,Fparents at all affected schools are
OL,9,Fbeing offered information about the
OL,10,Fsigns and symptoms.
OL,12,FThe agency is insisting that the risk
OL,13,Fto the wider public remains low.
OL,15,FDr Rachel Mearkle, consultant in
OL,16,Fhealth protection, said: "We
OL,17,Funderstand that many people will be
OL,18,Faffected by this sad news and would
OL,19,Flike to offer our condolences to the
OL,20,Ffriends and family of this student.
OL,26,@xD@ZOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1778937070
OL,3,CStudent dies and two others being
OL,4,Ctreated after meningitis outbreak in
OL,5,CReading
OL,7,F"Students and staff will naturally be
OL,8,Ffeeling worried about the likelihood
OL,9,Fof further cases, however
OL,10,Fmeningococcal meningitis requires very
OL,11,Fclose contact to spread and large
OL,12,Foutbreaks as we saw in Kent recently,
OL,13,Fare thankfully rare.
OL,15,F"We are working closely with partners
OL,16,Fand have provided public health advice
OL,17,Fand precautionary antibiotic treatment
OL,18,Fto close contacts of the cases.
OL,19,FMeningococcal disease does not spread
OL,20,Feasily and the risk to the wider
OL,21,Fpublic remains low.
OL,26,@oD@AOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1778937070
OL,3,CStudent dies and two others being
OL,4,Ctreated after meningitis outbreak in
OL,5,CReading
OL,7,F"Anyone can get meningitis, and around
OL,8,F300 to 400 cases of meningococcal
OL,9,Fdisease are diagnosed in England every
OL,10,Fyear. It's most common in babies,
OL,11,Fyoung children, teenagers, and young
OL,12,Fadults.
OL,14,F"It needs to be treated quickly so it
OL,15,Fis important to know the signs and
OL,16,Fsymptoms. They can appear in any order
OL,17,Fand may not all be present, so seek
OL,18,Frapid medical attention if there is
OL,19,Fever any concern.
OL,26,@oD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1778937070
OL,3,CStudent dies and two others being
OL,4,Ctreated after meningitis outbreak in
OL,5,CReading
OL,7,F"Signs and symptoms of meningococcal
OL,8,Fmeningitis and sepsis can include a
OL,9,Ffever, headache, rapid breathing,
OL,10,Fdrowsiness, shivering, vomiting and
OL,11,Fcold hands and feet.
OL,13,F"Sepsis can also cause a
OL,14,Fcharacteristic rash that does not fade
OL,15,Fwhen pressed against a glass."
OL,26,@oD@AOUwD@^O]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
