OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1778937070
OL,3,CStudent dies and two others being
OL,4,Ctreated after meningitis outbreak in
OL,5,CReading
OL,7,FA spokesperson for Hart surgery in
OL,8,FHenley-on-Thames said: "We have been
OL,9,Fin contact with the UK Health Security
OL,10,FAgency this morning (14 May) regarding
OL,11,Fthe very sad news that a student at
OL,12,FHenley College has died with suspected
OL,13,Fmeningococcal disease.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1778937070
OL,3,CStudent dies and two others being
OL,4,Ctreated after meningitis outbreak in
OL,5,CReading
OL,7,F"They have confirmed that they are
OL,8,Factively contacting those who may be
OL,9,Fat risk due to a close association
OL,10,Fwith the student involved. If you have
OL,11,Fnot been contacted by The UK Health
OL,12,FSecurity Agency, then currently you do
OL,13,Fnot require any treatment. Staff and
OL,14,Fstudents have been advised they can
OL,15,Fattend the college as usual.
OL,17,F"The number of confirmed cases is very
OL,18,Flow so there are currently no plans
OL,19,Ffor a local emergency meningitis
OL,20,Fvaccination programme.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
